If you happen to use [Apache Commons Lang][1] then you can use [strip][2] and add all the characters you want.

    final String STRIPPED_CHARS = &quot; \t\u00A0\u1680\u180e\u2000\u200a\u202f\u205f\u3000&quot;;
    
